  m_text: You are a dwarf and you want to mine gold. You can do this by "attaking"
    it with the pickaxe, the drill or the dynamite you can throw by pressing space
    on your Keyboard. When you hae destroyed a stone you get gold and with that you
    can buy upgrades from the friendly merchant, which will increase your damage
    and weaponspeed. You can do that 3 times per tool and the price  will increase.
    When you are fully upgraded you have won the game. Congrats!
